data.description: Welcome to 3036 Horse Shoe Dr, Atlanta, where comfort and luxury harmonize in this stunning residence, boasting 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms!! Enter into the grandeur of the living and dining room area, offering a spacious and inviting atmosphere that sets the tone for modern living. The Owner suite features vaulted ceiling, custom walk-in closet, and a BRAND new opulent master bathroom, featuring a double vanity and an expansive tiled shower. Cocreating a private oasis for relaxation. Two additional generously sized bedrooms with massive walk-in closets. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, showcasing granite countertops, which features an suave island, electric cooktop, range hood, built-in microwave. Step out onto the fairly new deck, that complements the well maintain lawn, which is idea for outdoor enjoyment and entertaining. Gresham Park offers a desirable community and within a great school cluster. This home offers the perfect blend of convenience and luxury. Enjoy the convenience of walking to the newly built Walking Trail, and mins from major Interstates. Experience the epitome of modern living at 3036 Horse Shoe Dr. FHA approved *Open House 4/19/2024 6pm-8pm & 4/21/2024 @ 4pm-6pm*
